Happy Sunday all! Tonight we have a look at the next Dimensional object in my latest project series... the “Dimensional Tesseract”. 💎🌈⚡️✨ A piece truly not of this realm, this gem harnesses the Dimensional energy of the BiFrost in order to secure safe passage throughout the Nine-Realms... Supporting perfect cubic symmetry, this piece is made from the crystalline and Prismatic glass of the Rainbow Bridge itself... from just a glance or a touch, this gem is sure to bring good energy and vibes your way 🙏🙏⚡️🌈✨
💎💎💎
SWIPE LEFT for detail shots

Outstanding collaboration by @jsynlord x @mullerglass 🤩
SWIPE 👉👉 FOR 360 VID

The elegant shaping of the transparent glass by Lord balances beautifully with Peter Muller’s renown voodoo style. 
Textures that remind you of soft rabbit fur, faded rust, and cloth, all have their own way of making you feel growth and decay at the same time. The shaping of the slicked back ears and stitch-work are only some of the details that you can get lost in. 
Popping colors from the carrot, a peeking bandage, vivid buttons on the side and on the bubble cap are the icing on the cake!

Along with the masterful color work, as demonstrated in the video, it does have recycling function to ensure this piece takes your breath away💨🥕🐰
Please send a DM for more purchase information 🤳🏼 Pics and Writeup by @juanlovesglass
